ance beam.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1142, \"end\": 1149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.8035275645000186e-12, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first Brazilian\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1209}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic event\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"female gymnasts\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"all four apparatus\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"reality\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1376}, {\"ngram\": \"the standings\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"a solid showing\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"the balance beam\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the uneven bars, Biles got too much air on her flip as she transitioned from the higher to the lower bar and had to bend both knees to avoid touching the ground.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1608, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the uneven bars\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"too much air\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"her flip\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"the lower bar\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"both knees\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1607}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also needed to take an extra swing to continue her routine on the apparatus.\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an extra swing\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"her routine\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"the apparatus\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After completing her dismount, she looked really annoyed at herself for making the error as she walked off the mat.\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her dismount\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"the error\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"the mat\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Awarded 13.733 points, it was the worst score she had earned across all her performances to date in Paris.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1908, \"end\": 1913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2384573051219845e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"13.733 points\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"the worst score\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"all her performances\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"date\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact it was the only time she failed to breach the 14-point barrier.\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"the only time\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"the 14-point barrier\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not even know how I held on to that,\\\" Biles could be heard saying immediately after the fumble.\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"the fumble\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A mistake that could have proven costly turned out to be a mere blip in Biles' charge towards victory.\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A mistake\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"a mere blip\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles' charge\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2176}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By the time she stood at the edge of the mat to start her final performance, she knew the gold would be hers provided she avoided any major mishaps during her floor exercise display.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"the edge\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"the mat\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"her final performance\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2269}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2288}, {\"ngram\": \"any major mishaps\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2341}, {\"ngram\": \"her floor exercise display\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Competing last, Biles executed an electrifying routine to secure the gold with a total of 59.131 points.\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2399}, {\"ngram\": \"an electrifying routine\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2432}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"a total\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"59.131 points\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles said having Andrade on her tail had made her nervous.\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2502, \"end\": 2509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.8035275645000186e-12, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2489}, {\"ngram\": \"her tail\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not want to compete with Rebecca no more.\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2576, \"end\": 2583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.995976762829015, \"rank\": 0.004039488993227354, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am tired.\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2604, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rebeca pushes me to be my best, she's a phenomenal athlete,\\\" Biles said.\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rebeca\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2611}, {\"ngram\": \"a phenomenal athlete\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2663}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's way too close.\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never had an athlete that close, so it definitely put me on my toes.\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2728}, {\"ngram\": \"my toes\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On each event we are very similar in scores.\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each event\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2792}, {\"ngram\": \"scores\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was like, 'okay, I think I have to bring out the big guns this time',\\\" added the American who opted to execute the more difficult Yurchenko double pike vault knowing that she would be pushed all the way by Andrade.\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 3040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2907, \"end\": 2915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7394245168701961, \"rank\": 0.35240301846696326, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2956, \"end\": 2965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"score\": 0.9924615128803714, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yurchenko\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\"}, {\"begin\": 3032, \"end\": 3039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.8035275645000186e-12, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the big guns\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a sign of great camaraderie, a beaming Andrade applauded Biles as soon as the American had struck the final pose of her floor routine, sitting on the mat with her left hand covering her face.\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3084, \"end\": 3091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.8035275645000186e-12, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}, {\"begin\": 3123, \"end\": 3131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7394245168701961, \"rank\": 0.35240301846696326, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sign\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3051}, {\"ngram\": \"great camaraderie\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3072}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"the final pose\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"her floor routine\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3178}, {\"ngram\": \"the mat\", \"from\": 3191, \"to\": 3198}, {\"ngram\": \"her left hand\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3217}, {\"ngram\": \"her face\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andrade did not need to wait for the score to flash up to know who would be crowned champion and quickly went up to hug Biles.\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3237, \"end\": 3244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.8035275645000186e-12, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the score\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3279}, {\"ngram\": \"champion\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3329}, {\"ngram\": \"hug Biles\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was really cool, knowing that I made her work, right?\\\"\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her work\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andrade said of Biles.\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3424, \"end\": 3431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.8035275645000186e-12, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's an honour to be able to compete next to her.\\\"\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an honour\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brazilian earned a second successive silver in the event, having finished behind Biles' teammateSunisa Leein Tokyo.\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Brazilian\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3513}, {\"ngram\": \"a second successive silver\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3547}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3560}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles' teammateSunisa Leein Tokyo\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lee fought back from a disappointing start on the vault to claim the bronze with 56.465 points.\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3621, \"end\": 3624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9999994690644189, \"rank\": 5.309357564245988e-07, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a disappointing start\", \"from\": 3642, \"to\": 3663}, {\"ngram\": \"the vault\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3676}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze\", \"from\": 3686, \"to\": 3696}, {\"ngram\": \"56.465 points\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Tokyo, Biles withdrew from the event to prioritise her mental health after suffering from the \\\"twisties\\\", a condition involving the temporary loss of spatial awareness that some gymnasts can experience when executing high-difficulty elements.\", \"from\": 3718, \"to\": 3963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3721, \"end\": 3726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999482320177, \"rank\": 5.176760420852733e-08, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\